Birthdays are celebrated annually worldwide but for comedian Bovi, that will no longer be applicable. He has revealed plans to celebrate his birthday weekly. The organiser of the popular stand-up comedy concert, ‘Bovi: Man on Fire’ made this known in an Instagram post. The 42-year-old comic star disclosed he was born on a Tuesday.   Silence has a golden voice, says Actor Ugezu     Don’t marry if you aren’t a millionaire, Joro Olumofin…     Every man wants me, says BBNaija’s Maria   - Advertisement - He wished himself a happy birthday on the day while listing all the things he intends to do every Tuesday in 2022. Bovi wrote: “This year, I will be marking my birthdays weekly. I was born on a Tuesday. “That’s 2,206 weeks ago. So, there it goes; happy birthday to me! “To celebrate my birthday today, I will baff, eat, watch TV, plan my life and pray to see another Tuesday!”